の伝説を作る』……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":6,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":6,"voiceId":"event239-02-017","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":6}],"windowDisplayName":"蘭","body":"『G.B.T.優勝』だけが、わかりやすい目標で。\nだから今、時間がないなりに\nみんな一生懸命、全力でいられるんだと思う","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":6,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":6,"voiceId":"event239-02-018","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":6}],"windowDisplayName":"蘭","body":"でも、今でさえみんなの予定が合わないのに、\n進学したり、仕事するようになったらきっと\nバンドの存在がもっと薄れてく気がする","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":6,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":6,"voiceId":"event239-02-019","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":6}],"windowDisplayName":"蘭","body":"大人になったあたしたちの『いつも通り』が\nバンドって形じゃなくなるのかもって、そう思って……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":6,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":6,"voiceId":"event239-02-020","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":7}],"windowDisplayName":"モカ","body":"…………","tention